            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-01/20220123_news_pacquiao.jpg?VersionId=zuSqxbz8fVbKHHLcIxErYyqbRevM6Dp4&amp;h=486901c9&amp;itok=eyWgFARm" title="前拳王帕奎奥现在是菲律宾参议员，他将竞选菲律宾总统。（法新社）" alt="前拳王帕奎奥现在是菲律宾参议员，他将竞选菲律宾总统。（法新社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-01/20220123_news_pacquiao.jpg?VersionId=zuSqxbz8fVbKHHLcIxErYyqbRevM6Dp4&amp;h=486901c9&amp;itok=eyWgFARm" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
